Thanks to all of you who support us every day from all over the world! 🙏 

We are pleased to meet you with your recipes, your passions, your stories. 🍸 

Every day we are lucky enough to talk to many of you, and we are sorry if sometimes we are unable to answer everyone in time but you are so many. 

Remember to use our official Hashtag to give us the opportunity to find you, and to grow with you! 💪 

In this video we thank some of the many friends with whom we have shared many posts! 👋 

Thank you all, and we hope to be back very soon, all stronger than ever! ❤ 

Salute! 🍸🍸🍸 

